test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x78a8bc9ff500>([-23])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x78a8bc9ff500> = [[1], [1, -23], [-23, 1], [-23, 1, -23], [1], [1, -23], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -1 == -23
 +  where -1 = <built-in function prod>([-1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
